---
// src/components/Testimonials.astro
---
<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 bg-slate-50">
  <div class="text-center mb-16">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">Ce qu'en pensent nos clients</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">La satisfaction de nos utilisateurs est notre meilleure publicité.</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
    <!-- Avis 1 -->
    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 flex flex-col justify-between">
      <div>
        <div class="flex text-amber-400 mb-4">
          <!-- 5 stars -->
          {[1,2,3,4,5].map(() => (
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/></svg>
          ))}
        </div>
        <p class="text-slate-600 italic mb-6">"Le nouveau site est incroyablement rapide ! Le score Lighthouse est à 100 partout, et nos taux de conversion ont explosé."</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-700 font-bold">JD</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-sm">Jean Dupont</h4>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs">Directeur Marketing</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Avis 2 -->
    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 flex flex-col justify-between">
      <div>
        <div class="flex text-amber-400 mb-4">
          {[1,2,3,4,5].map(() => (
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/></svg>
          ))}
        </div>
        <p class="text-slate-600 italic mb-6">"Le design avec Tailwind CSS est parfaitement adapté à notre charte graphique. L'équipe a fait un travail remarquable sur le responsive."</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center text-teal-700 font-bold">ML</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-sm">Marie Leroy</h4>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs">Fondatrice Startup</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Avis 3 -->
    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 flex flex-col justify-between">
      <div>
        <div class="flex text-amber-400 mb-4">
          {[1,2,3,4,5].map(() => (
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/></svg>
          ))}
        </div>
        <p class="text-slate-600 italic mb-6">"L'utilisation d'Astro combiné avec du Markdown pour notre blog a rendu la création de contenu si simple et agréable."</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-violet-100 flex items-center justify-center text-violet-700 font-bold">LM</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-sm">Lucas Martin</h4>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs">Créateur de Contenu</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
